MBOMBELA &#8211; A male driving an F-Type Jaguar sports car has been arrested this morning at around 07:30 on the N4 Road for driving at 231 kilometers near Alkmaar.Department of Community Safety, Security and Liaison spokesman Mr Joseph Mabuza said the man has been taken to the Nelspruit Police Station for detention before his court appearance.&#8220;He will be charged for Reckless and Negligent driving.&#8221;MEC Pat Ngomane applaud the two officers for such a great work, saying that suicidal drivers should be removed from the road as they also put the lives of other road users in danger.Read more here: Huge traffic, many arrests, few fatalities on Lowveld s roads